Definition: epiphytic cactus of Brazilian ancestry widely cultivated as a houseplant having jointed flat segments and usually rose-purple flowers that bloom in winter
Synonyms: Schlumbergera_buckleyi, Schlumbergera_baridgesii, cactus, genus_Schlumbergera, m, epiphytic, of, Brazilian, ancestry, widely, cultivated, as, a, houseplant, having, jointed, flat, segments, and, usually, rose-purple, flowers, that, bloom, in, winter
Category: noun.plant
